| Snippet name | README section |
|---|---|
| `MessagesEntraIdAuth` | Authenticate the client → Using Microsoft Entra ID |
| `MessagesCreateConversation` | Examples → Create a conversation thread |
| `MessagesSendConversationMessage` | Examples → Send a message in a conversation thread |
| `MessagesListConversations` | Examples → List conversation threads |
| `MessagesSendInteractive` | Examples → Send an interactive message |
| `MessagesSendReaction` | Examples → Send a reaction message |

